christopher paul " chris " gardner ( born february 9 , 1954 ) is an american entrepreneur , investor , stockbroker , motivational speaker , author , and philanthropist who , during the early 1980s , struggled with homelessness while raising his toddler son , christopher , jr. gardner 's book of memoirs , the pursuit of happyness , was published in may 2006 .

movies : will smith is struggling single father chris gardner in this film based on a true story

